{"tid":672077,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州地鐵測試：Apple Pay快QR code四倍","createTime":"2018-05-20T16:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T06:54:17.000Z","uid":144372,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"52c72f61c8824cdff5577e6058e671f56b0c1dac","tid":672077,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/704346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifanr.com%2F704346&d=%2FsUZROYJCtj%2BNbeJc%2FSPlcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=670fd475\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ifanr.com/704346</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你見到一位路人在地鐵閘口前拿出銀行卡或者手機，他不一定是拿錯了。因為，用銀行卡或者手機搭地鐵，終於在今天成為現實。<br />\n<br />\n8 月 18 日上午，廣州地鐵移動支付及金融 IC 卡項目儀式啟動。即日起，廣州地鐵 APM 線成為國內首條支持直接刷 Apple Pay 等銀聯&ldquo;雲閃付&rdquo;和金融 IC 卡付費過閘的地鐵線路。按計劃到 2016 年底，廣州地鐵全線網各站將陸續實現上述功能。不過銀聯閃付雲閃付在地鐵之前，已經和出租車以及廣州 6 條公交線路有布點合作。<br />\n<br />\n項目由人民銀行廣州分行、廣州地鐵和廣東銀聯聯合推出，只要用戶持有支持小額免密的銀聯&ldquo;雲閃付&rdquo;手機（包括 Apple Pay，Android HCE 等）或者帶有&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;標志的金融 IC 卡，都可以直接刷手機或銀行卡過閘，不需要預先購票或者充值。<br />\n<br />\nDSC03569<br />\n<br />\n刷手機、刷銀行卡，請走專用通道<br />\n<br />\n今日下午，愛範兒（微信號：ifanr）也親身體驗了一把這種搭乘地鐵的&ldquo;新姿勢&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n攜帶著一台開通了Apple Pay 的 iPhone 手機、一台開通了 Samsung Pay 的三星手機還有一張有&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;字樣的銀聯銀行卡，愛範兒分別測試了四種地鐵票支付方式。<br />\n<br />\ndt2<br />\n<br />\n測試地點是 APM 線的廣州塔站，普通入閘口的右側有一條移動支付專用通道。專用通道入口設置有讀取器，分為有&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;字樣的感應區和二維碼掃碼區。<br />\n<br />\n1，Apple Pay 支付：愛範兒首先測試開通了Apple Pay 的 iPhone 手機。剛把手機靠近&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;感應區，屏幕就出現檢驗 Touch ID 指紋的要求，<ins><strong>通過指紋檢驗後閘口馬上打開，響應時間不超過 2 秒</strong></ins>。整個過程和平時用 Apple Pay 到便利店支付一樣。<br />\n<br />\n2，Samsung Pay 支付：愛範兒用同樣方法測試開通了 Samsung Pay 的三星手機，但手機界面沒有響應，閘口沒有打開但出亮紅燈。愛範兒采訪了在場的一位地鐵工作人員，她表示今天也有部分&ldquo;嘗鮮&rdquo;的乘客出現類似的支付失敗狀況，以 Android 手機為主，估計是因為系統還不穩定。<br />\n<br />\nDSC03575<br />\n<br />\n3，&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;銀聯卡支付：愛範兒也嘗試了使用有銀聯&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;功能的銀行卡。銀行卡在感應區停留不到一秒，閘門就應聲打開，讓人有一種使用羊城通的錯覺。<br />\n<br />\nDSC03572<br />\n<br />\n4，二維碼支付：&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;感應區上方是二維碼掃碼器，愛範兒從打開支付寶頁面、打開付款二維碼、<strong><ins>把二維碼對準掃碼器、等待二維碼到支付成功花費約 8 秒時間，</ins></strong>閘門也順利打開。<br />\n<br />\n由於專用通道並不顯眼，使用移動支付專用通道的乘客不多。愛範兒在入閘處停留約 30 分鐘，只有 2 位乘客略顯笨拙地使用移動支付通道入閘。愛範兒隨機采訪的幾位匆匆通過普通通道的乘客，他們都表示對這種新的地鐵票支付方式並不知情。<br />\n<br />\n一位負責維持入口秩序的地鐵義工告訴愛範兒，從上午通道開通到愛範兒采訪時的下午 2 點 45 分，使用移動支付通道的乘客不到 10 位。考慮到采訪時段人流較少，在上下班高峰期移動支付通道的使用率估計會更高。"},{"pid":"4dfa33447d70886810328f07bfdb6955dabd3235","tid":672077,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"深圳上星期仲要開始推掃碼入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d209ce69938b3f78e806b32e6471410cc4298137","tid":672077,"uid":138502,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"舊科技 (RFID) ： 1秒內入閘 連停都唔洗停 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0084afa2559c8e4acec24deab6ef76882693b97","tid":672077,"uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dfa33447d70886810328f07bfdb6955dabd3235","tid":672077,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"深圳上星期仲要開始推掃碼入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"港鐵職員入嚟睇啦"},{"pid":"b8fda7e4c4736a92d990d4fe107589bdca957717","tid":672077,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66373cf623726bf75b4d9ab084e2552ec48521c0","tid":672077,"uid":57214,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d0084afa2559c8e4acec24deab6ef76882693b97","tid":672077,"uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4dfa33447d70886810328f07bfdb6955dabd3235","tid":672077,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"深圳上星期仲要開始推掃碼入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"港鐵職員入嚟睇啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"@姐打羅夫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cc0e74fa1a51e4e864ac1ed2c9e7d2d616d908","tid":672077,"uid":158613,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:26:28.000Z","msg":"唔用QR code ,越嚟越落後了"},{"pid":"2d79d2b88d9bb6ab99fee3d6414643b7302c1bdc","tid":672077,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a7f11271e52ad0a8d4e81f00a94d11970b9895","tid":672077,"uid":25952,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"港鐵 港共表示：apply pay? 要奶共 不了"},{"pid":"76988961eb06378e44a522b87d5c72047d60935f","tid":672077,"uid":47359,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">QR code打手<br />\n1D wade<br />\n2群龍共舞<br />\n3姐打羅夫<br />\n4賈雨村<br />\n5人生鍾嘉欣<br />\n6上坂堇</span>"},{"pid":"24fb4fca896ca176fb71ec54c56b873472d2df7b","tid":672077,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:45:03.000Z","msg":"支那又要安檢加埋QR人多真係無半個鐘唔使入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6812f543fcb4644cfd1cd525fdb066956e3585bc","tid":672077,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BE%8A%E5%9F%8E%E9%80%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25BE%258A%25E5%259F%258E%25E9%2580%259A&d=%2FsUZROYJCtj%2BNbeJc%2FSPlcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=a42087b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BE%8A%E5%9F%8E%E9%80%9A</a><br />\n<br />\n用羊城通有折, 點解唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fce45a9b183e077598c8d30b38d671f4b9628a5","tid":672077,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>NFC 急速蠶食二維碼地位？<br />\n去年廣州地鐵已經開通刷二維碼過閘服務，這次開通銀聯移動支付及金融IC 卡付後，將同時支持二維碼、銀聯&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;、金融IC卡和NFC 手機票等多種移動支付手段。<br />\n<br />\n而近年被認為是移動支付未來的 NFC 手機支付方式，最受外界關注。<br />\n<br />\nNFC 是 Near Field Communication 縮寫，即近距離無線通訊技術。這個技術由非接觸式射頻識別（RFID）演變而來，由飛利浦半導體（現恩智浦半導體公司）、諾基亞和索尼共同研製開發，其基礎是 RFID 及互連技術。<br />\n<br />\nNFC 手機指帶有 NFC 模塊的手機，它能直接感應收付款讀取器而不需要經過刷碼等繁瑣程序。使用者只需要把手機靠近讀取器就能完成支付，和傳統條形碼、二維碼等掃碼支付相比，節省了&ldquo;打開支付碼界面&rdquo;、&ldquo;掃碼&rdquo;這兩個步驟，支付便利性大增。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港真係個笑話<br />\n行慢人幾步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fc62f59fc8032cd5f248aaa6743727f8b632af","tid":672077,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T19:25:33.000Z","msg":"30分鐘已有2位使用移動支付<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b7cd41e448781a8106d7520c8a7743f8cf474b","tid":672077,"uid":10064,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1fce45a9b183e077598c8d30b38d671f4b9628a5","tid":672077,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>NFC 急速蠶食二維碼地位？<br />\n去年廣州地鐵已經開通刷二維碼過閘服務，這次開通銀聯移動支付及金融IC 卡付後，將同時支持二維碼、銀聯&ldquo;閃付&rdquo;、金融IC卡和NFC 手機票等多種移動支付手段。<br />\n<br />\n而近年被認為是移動支付未來的 NFC 手機支付方式，最受外界關注。<br />\n<br />\nNFC 是 Near Field Communication 縮寫，即近距離無線通訊技術。這個技術由非接觸式射頻識別（RFID）演變而來，由飛利浦半導體（現恩智浦半導體公司）、諾基亞和索尼共同研製開發，其基礎是 RFID 及互連技術。<br />\n<br />\nNFC 手機指帶有 NFC 模塊的手機，它能直接感應收付款讀取器而不需要經過刷碼等繁瑣程序。使用者只需要把手機靠近讀取器就能完成支付，和傳統條形碼、二維碼等掃碼支付相比，節省了&ldquo;打開支付碼界面&rdquo;、&ldquo;掃碼&rdquo;這兩個步驟，支付便利性大增。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港真係個笑話<br />\n行慢人幾步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:35:59.000Z","msg":"科技發展落後唔係因為人材，係因為要奶共"},{"pid":"063dcef04db0503b6662a6d08d6e48eb1a60dac1","tid":672077,"uid":74361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:37:48.000Z","msg":"呢次真係贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1473c6d52c2c3222065ff122525bf3ed07bbb2fc","tid":672077,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:40:29.000Z","msg":"mtr反應仲慢過IE"},{"pid":"18d31fed2c372d41ea4f8ede0a5eb4de0192c0c4","tid":672077,"uid":2270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:40:57.000Z","msg":"八達通我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f4d8c005a686f5c811e0e8dae05a7bb768990b","tid":672077,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e283bedfb05bbd5340a5a632924372d2b4819953","tid":672077,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:45:14.000Z","msg":"我就當你拎堆個QRCode去閘口係一秒攪掂<br />\n<br />\n開app load code唔係時間<br />\n<br />\n我係褲袋拎張卡出黎直接do唔好<br />\n<br />\n仲要講緊轉左手機掃qr code安全性係無提高到"},{"pid":"c8905a38153d1151dc8767e9646617abf104949c","tid":672077,"uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"76988961eb06378e44a522b87d5c72047d60935f","tid":672077,"uid":47359,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">QR code打手<br />\n1D wade<br />\n2群龍共舞<br />\n3姐打羅夫<br />\n4賈